### Narrative Review

#### [MODIFY] [narrative_review.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/narrative_review.py)

**3. SRT-based naming in [save_character_bible_csv()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/narrative_review.py#649-676)** (line 649) and bible text save (line 790):
- Add optional `srt_stem` parameter to [save_character_bible_csv()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/narrative_review.py#649-676) and [run_character_pipeline()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/narrative_review.py#678-799)
- Change `_character_bible.csv` → `{srt_stem}_character_bible.csv`
- Change `_character_bible.txt` → `{srt_stem}_character_bible.txt`

